20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsyrian-rebels-reach-damascus-suburbs-threatening-assad-regime-2024-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erebels%20swept%20into%20Damascus%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20Syrian%20capital.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20insurgents%20declared%20the%20city%20%26quot%3Bfree%2C%26quot%3B%20Russia's%20foreign%20ministry%20announced%20Assad%20had%20resigned%20his%20position%20and%20left%20the%20country.%20Russian%20state%20news%20later%20reported%20that%20Assad%20had%20arrived%20in%20Moscow%2C%20where%20he%20was%20granted%20asylum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20collapse%20of%20Assad's%20government%20came%20after%20a%20coalition%20of%20opposition%20forces%20led%20by%20Hayat%20Tahrir%20al-Sham%20launched%20a%20surprise%20offensive%2C%20seizing%20control%20of%20major%20cities%20like%20Aleppo%2C%20Hama%2C%20and%20Homs%20in%20a%20matter%20of%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESyrians%20around%20the%20world%20celebrated%20the%20end%20of%20Assad's%20rule%2C%20which%20was%20marked%20by%20brutal%20suppression.%20His%20violent%20crackdown%20on%20peaceful%20anti-government%20protests%20in%202011%2C%20part%20of%20the%20Arab%20Spring%20uprisings%2C%20sparked%20a%20civil%20war%20that%20killed%20hundreds%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%20and%20displaced%20millions%2C%20straining%20neighboring%20countries%20like%20Turkey%20and%20Lebanon.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWorld%20leaders%20conveyed%20cautious%20optimism%20after%20news%20of%20Assad's%20ouster%2C%20but%20uncertainty%20remains%20around%20what%20kind%20of%20government%20and%20leader%20will%20replace%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20major%20player%20will%20almost%20certainly%20be%20HTS%2C%20which%20is%20led%20by%20Abu%20Mohammed%20al-Jolani%2C%20a%20Syrian%20who%20fought%20against%20US%20occupation%20in%20Iraq%20alongside%20a%20branch%20of%20Al%20Qaeda.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJolani%20later%20returned%20to%20Syria%2C%20his%20homeland%2C%20where%20he%20fought%20with%20Jabhat%20Al-Nusra%20%E2%80%94%20an%20Al%20Qaeda%20offshoot%20formed%20in%202012%20%E2%80%94%20and%20other%20rebel%20groups%20against%20Assad's%20forces.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJolani%20severed%20his%20ties%20with%20Al%20Qaeda%20in%202016%20and%20formed%20a%20new%20group%2C%20which%20eventually%20became%20HTS%20in%202017.%20Since%20then%2C%20Jolani%20has%20portrayed%20himself%20as%20a%20more%20moderate%20leader%20to%20gain%20international%20legitimacy.%20Both%20the%20United%20States%20and%20the%20United%20Nations%20still%20list%20HTS%20as%20a%20terrorist%20organization.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20one%202021%20interview%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.pbs.org%2Fwgbh%2Ffrontline%2Finterview%2Fabu-mohammad-al-jolani%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPBS%20Frontline%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Jolani%20called%20the%20group's%20terrorist%20designation%20a%20%26quot%3Bpolitical%20label%20that%20carries%20no%20truth%20or%20credibility.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThrough%20our%2010-year%20journey%20in%20this%20revolution%2C%20we%20haven't%20posed%20any%20threat%20to%20Western%20or%20European%20society%3A%20no%20security%20threat%2C%20no%20economic%20threat%2C%20nothing.%20That's%20why%20this%20designation%20is%20politicized%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20HTS%20has%20controlled%20Syria's%20northwestern%20Idlib%20Province%2C%20where%20analysts%20say%20it%20worked%20to%20consolidate%20power%20and%20transform%20its%20image%20while%20pursuing%20its%20ultimate%20goal%20of%20toppling%20Assad.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20Idlib%2C%20Jolani%20established%20the%20so-called%20Syrian%20Salvation%20Government%2C%20which%20has%20acted%20as%20a%20showcase%20for%20what%20his%20leadership%20could%20bring%20to%20a%20wider%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20about%20the%20Salvation%20Government%20in%20the%20PBS%20interview%2C%20Jolani%20said%20that%20while%20the%20situation%20in%20Idlib%20was%20not%20ideal%2C%20there%20was%20%26quot%3Ba%20self-asserting%20model%20that%20was%20capable%20of%20running%20the%20affairs%20of%20a%20whole%20country%20under%20an%20Islamic%20rule.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20some%20have%20remained%20doubtful%20that%20the%20group%20has%20fully%20cut%20its%20links%20with%20Al%20Qaeda%2C%20it%20has%20put%20forth%20a%20message%20of%20inclusiveness%20and%20unity%20in%20recent%20days%2C%20calling%20for%20a%20peaceful%20transition%20of%20power%20and%20reassuring%20religious%20and%20ethnic%20minorities%20in%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20the%20future%20Syria%20%E2%80%A6%20diversity%20is%20our%20strength%2C%20not%20a%20weakness%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20group%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20to%20the%20Kurdish%20minority%20in%20Aleppo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAron%20Lund%2C%20a%20fellow%20at%20Century%20International%20and%20a%20Middle%20East%20analyst%20at%20the%20Swedish%20Defense%20Research%20Agency%2C%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Fwho-are-the-syrian-rebels-claiming-control-of-damascus-13265314%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESky%20News%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20while%20Jolani%20and%20his%20group%20had%20changed%2C%20they%20remained%20%26quot%3Bpretty%20hardline.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20PR%2C%20but%20the%20fact%20they%20are%20engaging%20in%20this%20effort%20at%20all%20shows%20they%20are%20no%20longer%20as%20rigid%20as%20they%20once%20were%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20referencing%20video%20footage%20showing%20Jolani%20forbidding%20fighters%20from%20entering%20homes%20and%20telling%20them%20to%20protect%20citizens.%20%26quot%3BOld-school%20Al%20Qaeda%20or%20the%20Islamic%20State%20would%20never%20have%20done%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHTS%20is%20only%20one%20part%20of%20an%20ideologically%20diverse%20opposition%2C%20and%20it%20remains%20to%20be%20seen%20if%20the%20coalition%20can%20peacefully%20share%20power%20and%20extend%20unified%20control%20over%20the%20whole%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20not%2C%20intra-Syrian%20territorial%20fragmentation%2C%20and%20the%20potential%20emergence%20of%20regional%20warlords%20and%20fiefdoms%2C%20will%20quickly%20grow%2C%26quot%3B%20Jonathan%20Panikoff%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Scowcroft%20Middle%20East%20Security%20Initiative%20at%20the%20Atlantic%20Council's%20Middle%20East%20Program%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-we-know-about-hayat-tahrir-al-sham-syria-rebels-2024-12%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733688849000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6755c0d2a57635a3d24d00f7%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-we-know-about-hayat-tahrir-al-sham-syria-rebels-2024-12%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20organization%2C%20which%20the%20US%20designates%20a%20terrorist%20group%2C%20has%20tried%20to%20shed%20that%20image%20and%20appear%20more%20moderate%20to%20the%20West.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22nrennolds%40insider.com%20(Nathan%20Rennolds)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A65%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-we-know-about-hayat-tahrir-al-sham-syria-rebels-2024-12%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'Fundamental%20act%20of%20justice'%3A%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20on%20fall%20of%20Assad%20govt%20in%20Syria%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733687877000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116115449%2Cimgsize-39582.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ffundamental-act-of-justice-us-president-joe-biden-on-fall-of-assad-government-in-syria%2Farticleshow%2F116115389.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F116115389.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EUS%20President%20Biden%20declared%20the%20Assad%20regime's%20collapse%20in