the%20TASS%20and%20Ria%20Novosti%20news%20agencies.%20%26quot%3BRussia%20granted%20them%20asylum%20on%20humanitarian%20grounds%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20buzz%20on%20social%20media%20with%20flight%20trackers%20speculating%20the%20mysterious%20whereabouts%20of%20Assad%20for%20most%20part%20of%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20Syrian%20Air%20plane%20took%20off%20from%20Damascus%20airport%20around%20the%20time%20the%20capital%20was%20taken%20by%20rebels%2C%20according%20to%20data%20from%20the%20Flightradar%20website.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20aircraft%20initially%20flew%20towards%20Syria's%20coastal%20region%2C%20a%20stronghold%20of%20Assad's%20Alawite%20sect%2C%20but%20then%20made%20an%20abrupt%20U-turn%20and%20flew%20in%20the%20opposite%20direction%20for%20a%20few%20minutes%20before%20disappearing%20off%20the%20map.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20sudden%20change%20in%20course%20and%20disappearance%20of%20the%20plane%20from%20tracking%20could%20indicate%20it%20had%20been%20shot%20down%2C%20or%20that%20it%20had%20switched%20off%20its%20transponder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20Assad%20and%20family%20in%20Russia%20now%2C%20it%20is%20clear%20the%20plane%20had%20switched%20off%20its%20transponder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAssad's%20departure%20comes%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%20after%20the%20Islamist%20Hayat%20Tahrir%20al-Sham%20(HTS)%20group%20challenged%20more%20than%20five%20decades%20of%20the%20Assad%20family%20rule%20with%20a%20lightning%20offensive.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%2050%20years%20of%20oppression%20under%20Baath%20rule%2C%20and%2013%20years%20of%20crimes%20and%20tyranny%20and%20displacement...%20we%20announce%20today%20the%20end%20of%20this%20dark%20period%20and%20the%20start%20of%20a%20new%20era%20for%20Syria%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20rebel%20factions%20said%20on%20Telegram.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Islamist%20leader%20of%20HTS%2C%20Abu%20Mohammed%20al-Jolani%2C%20visited%20the%20capital%20Damascus's%20landmark%20Umayyad%20Mosq