ro%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Salt%20Typhoon%20telecom%20hack%20targeted%20senior%20American%20political%20figures%2C%20the%20White%20House%20says%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228256%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22computer%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F675207ec8fb3f94e5073b0f4%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225504%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20government%20started%20investigating%20the%20Salt%20Typhoon%20hack%20after%20Microsoft%20sounded%20the%20alarm%20about%20irregularities.%3Cp%3Ed3sign%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Salt%20Typhoon%20hack%20is%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20attacks%20on%20US%20telecommunications%20ever%2C%20officials%20say.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20yearslong%20attack%20originated%20in%20China%20and%20targeted%20major%20telecom%20companies%20like%20AT%26amp%3BT%20and%20Verizon.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20NSA%20says%20it%20believes%20Chinese%20hackers%20were%20targeting%20senior%20US%20political%20figures.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUS%20security%20officials%20have%20warned%20that%20millions%20of%20people's%20personal%20information%20could%20be%20at%20risk%20after%20a%20yearslong%20hacking%20campaign%20originating%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20government%20started%20investigating%20the%20hack%20in%20the%20summer%20after%20Microsoft%20%E2%80%94%20which%20named%20the%20hack%20the%20Salt%20Typhoon%20%E2%80%94%20sounded%20alarms%20about%20anomalies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20to%20reporters%20on%20Saturday%2C%20White%20House%20Deputy%20national%20security%20advisor%20Anne%20Neuberger%20said%20that%20while%20data%20belonging%20to%20millions%20of%20Americans%20was%20likely%20compromised%2C%20the%20hack%20targeted%20senior%20US%20officials.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20the%20calls%20they%20recorded%20and%20took%20was%20really%20more%20focused%20on%20very%20senior%20political%20individuals%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20report%20from%20the%20Congressional%20Research%20Office%20said%20Chinese%20hackers%20may%20have%20sought%20access%20to%20presidential%20candidates'%20communications.%20%26quot%3BWith%20that%20access%2C%20they%20could%20potentially%20retrieve%20unencrypted%20communication%20(e.g.%2C%20voice%20calls%20and%20text%20messages)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20senior%20NSA%20official%20said%20in%20October%20that%20hackers%20from%20China%20accessed%20information%20from%20AT%26amp%3BT%2C%20Verizon%2C%20and%20Lumen%20Technologies%2C%20according%20to%20NBC.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESenate%20Intelligence%20Committee%20Chairman%20Mark%20Warner%20told%20The%20Washington%20Post%20that%20the%20hack%20is%20the%20%26quot%3Bworst%20telecom%20hack%20in%20our%20nation's%20history%20by%20far.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20an%20ongoing%20effort%20by%20China%20to%20infiltrate%20telecom%20systems%20around%20the%20world%2C%20to%20exfiltrate%20huge%20amounts%20of%20data%2C%26quot%3B%20Warner%20told%20the%20outlet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20New%20York%20Times%20reported%20that%20hackers%20from%20China%20went%20undetected%20inside%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatt-cellular-outage-sos-phone-service-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20telecommunications%20companies%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20over%20a%20year%20and%20obtained%20a%20nearly%20complete%20list%20of%20phone%20numbers%20that%20the%20Justice%20Department%20monitors%20in%20its%20%26quot%3Blawful%20intercept%26quot%3B%20system.%20The%20lawful%20intercept%20system%20is%20what%20allows%20law%20enforcement%2C%20through%20a%20court%20order%2C%20to%20wiretap%20or%20%26quot%3Bbug%26quot%3B%20phone%20calls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20FBI%20warned%20that%20all%20US%20citizens%20should%20use%20a%20cellphone%20that%20automatically%20updates%20its%20operating%20system%20and%20use%20encryption%20and%20multifactor%