-sunil-manohar-gavaskar-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESunil%20Gavaskar%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20urged%20India%20not%20to%20%26quot%3Bwaste%26quot%3B%20time%20in%20their%20hotel%20rooms%20after%20the%20early%20finish%20of%20the%20pink%20ball%20Test%2C%20but%20utilise%20the%20two%20extra%20days%20by%20sweating%20it%20out%20in%20training%20so%20they%20can%20bounce%20back%20in%20the%20third%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20were%20thoroughly%20exposed%20in%20their%2010-wicket%20loss%20in%20the%20second%20Test%20of%20the%20Border%20Gavaskar%20Trophy%20with%20the%20match%20ending%20in%20less%20than%20two-and-a-half%20days%20as%20Australia%20bounced%20back%20to%20level%20the%20five-game%20series%201-1.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%20at%20the%20remainder%20of%20the%20series%20as%20a%20three-match%20series.%20Forget%20it%20was%20a%20five-Test%20series.%20What%20I%20would%20like%20this%20Indian%20team%20to%20do%20is%20use%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20days%20for%20practice%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20told%20the%20official%20broadcaster.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20important.%20You%20can't%20be%20sitting%20in%20your%20hotel%20room%20or%20wherever%20you're%20going%20because%20you%20have%20come%20here%20to%20play%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20don't%20have%20to%20practice%20the%20whole%20day.%20You%20can%20practice%20a%20session%20in%20the%20morning%20or%20afternoon%2C%20whichever%20time%20you%20choose%2C%20but%20do%20not%20waste%20these%20days.%20You%20would%20have%20been%20here%20playing%20a%20Test%20match%20if%20the%20Test%20match%20were%20to%20go%20on%20for%20five%20days%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20third%20Test%20begins%20on%20December%2014%20and%20Gavaskar%20said%20the%20Indians%20should%20utilise%20the%20intervening%20time%20to%20get%20their%20rhythm%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733668260000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fpc3jguq_sc_625x300_08_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fhow-can-india-qualify-for-world-test-championship-final-after-loss-vs-australia-in-pink-ball-test-7201891%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20Indian%20cricket%20team's%20hopes%20of%20reaching%20the%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%20Final%20suffered%20a%20major%20blow%20after%20a%20humiliating%20loss%20to%20Australia%20in%20the%20pink-ball%20Test%20in%20Adelaide.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A19%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Faustralia-vs-india-2024-25%2Fhow-can-india-qualify-for-world-test-championship-final-after-loss-vs-australia-in-pink-ball-test-7201891%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Indians%20In%20Syria%20Are%20Safe%2C%20Embassy%20Operational%20In%20Damascus%3A%20Sources%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20embassy%20in%20war-torn%20Syria's%20capital%20Damascus%20continues%20to%20remain%20operational%20and%20is%20in%20touch%20with%20all%20Indian%20nationals%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20Indian%20nationals%20in%20Syria%20are%20safe%20and%20the%20embassy%20remains%20available%20to%20help%20them%2C%20sources%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIslamist-led%20rebels%20today%20said%20they%20have%20liberated%20Syria%20from%20the%20regime%20of%20Bashar%20al-Assad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20advisory%20earlier%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20(MEA)%20asked%20Indians%20living%20in%20the%20violence-hit%20country%20to%20leave%20by%20the%20earliest%20available%20commercial%20flights%20if%20they%20can.%20The%20advisory%20came%20before%20the%20rebels%20breached%20the%20capital%20Damascus.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20view%20of%20the%20situation%20prevailing%20in%20Syria%2C%20Indian%20nationals%20are%20advised%20to%20avoid%20all%20travel%20to%20Syria%2C%20until%20further%20notification%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20MEA%20had