o%20Damascus%20less%20than%20two%20weeks%20into%20a%20lightning%20offensive%20declaring%20they%20had%20toppled%20%26quot%3Btyrant%26quot%3B%20Assad%2C%20whose%20whereabouts%20are%20unknown%20after%20he%20reportedly%20fled%20Syria.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20statement%20that%20was%20read%20on%20Syrian%20state%20television%2C%20which%20rebels%20took%20over%2C%20quoted%20Jolani%20as%20saying%3A%20%26quot%3BWe%20continue%20to%20work%20with%20determination%20to%20achieve%20the%20goals%20of%20our%20revolution...%20We%20are%20determined%20to%20complete%20the%20path%20we%20started%20in%202011%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20year%2C%20Assad%20cracked%20down%20on%20peaceful%20pro-democracy%20protesters%2C%20triggering%20a%20complex%20conflict%20that%20drew%20in%20foreign%20armies%20and%20jihadists.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWith%20inputs%20from%20AFP%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733668020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F099ua6so_syria_625x300_08_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findians-in-syria-are-safe-embassy-operational-in-damascus-sources-7201782%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Indian%20embassy%20in%20war-torn%20Syria's%20capital%20Damascus%20continues%20to%20remain%20operational%20and%20is%20in%20touch%20with%20all%20Indian%20nationals%2C%20sources%20have%20said.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findians-in-syria-are-safe-embassy-operational-in-damascus-sources-7201782%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Deport%20all%20Illegal%20immigrants%2C%20exit%20Nato%2C%20pardon%20Jan%206%20defendants%3A%20Trump%20lays%20out%20his%20agenda%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733667293000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-116108851%2Cimgsize-66336.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.ind