%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tax%20contribution%20of%20petroleum%20sector%20set%20to%20drop%20rapidly%20in%20FY%202024-25%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733665053000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Ftax-contribution-of-petroleum-sector-set-to-drop-rapidly-in-fy-2024-25-124120800413_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Collections%20from%20windfall%20tax%20collections%20had%20cooled%20before%20it%20was%20withdrawn%20on%20December%202%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A4%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Feconomy%2Fnews%2Ftax-contribution-of-petroleum-sector-set-to-drop-rapidly-in-fy-2024-25-124120800413_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%222%2C500-km%20Chase%2C%20China%20Firm%20That%20Scammed%20Indians%3A%20How%20Cops%20Caught%20Trafficker%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20man%20who%20forced%20many%20young%20men%20from%20India%20to%20commit%20cyber%20crimes%20through%20fake%20call%20centres%20on%20the%20promise%20of%20getting%20them%20jobs%20abroad%20has%20been%20arrested%20from%20Hyderabad%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20yesterday%20after%20a%202%2C500-km%20chase.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKamran%20Haider%20alias%20Zaidi%20carried%20a%20reward%20of%20Rs%202%20lakh%20on%20information%20leading%20to%20his%20arrest%2C%20declared%20by%20the%20National%20Investigation%20Agency.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EZaidi%20and%20his%20accomplices%20used%20to%20traffic%20vulnerable%20young%20Indian%20men%20to%20the%20Golden%20Triangle%20Region%20in%20Southeast%20Asia%2C%20where%20the%20borders%20of%20Thailand%2C%20Laos%20and%20Myanmar%20meet%2C%20and%20force%20them%20to%20work%20in%20Chinese%20companies.%20Their%20passports%20would%20be%20taken%20away%20as%20soon%20as%20these%20men%20reached%20abroad%20and%20they%20would%20be%20forced%20into%20cyber%20crimes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Delhi%20Police%2C%20Zaidi%20was%20constantly%20changing%20his%20location%20and%20the%20police%20had%20deployed%20teams%20in%20Maharashtra%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20and%20Chhattisgarh%20to%20catch%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20manual%20inputs%20and%20technical%20surveillance%2C%20Zaidi's%20location%20was%20finally%20traced%20to%20Hyderabad.%20%26quot%3BHe%20was%20arrested%20after%20a%20long%20persevering%20chase%20of%202%2C500%20kilometres%20by%20the%20team%20without%20any%20rest%20near%20Nampally%20Railway%20Station%20in%20Hyderabad%20while%20he%20was%20trying%20to%20escape%20another%20hideout%2C%26quot%3B%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Special%20Cell)%20Manoj%20C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20scam%20came%20to%20light%20after%20a%20First%20Information%20Report%20(FIR)%20was%20registered%20in%20New%20Friends%20Colony%20in%20Delhi%20on%20the%20complaint%20of%20a%20person%20named%20Naresh%20Lakhwat%20on%20May%2027.%20He%20had%20told%20the%20police%20that%20he%20was%20looking%20for%20a%20job%20when%20he%20came%20across%20a%20consultancy%20firm%20called%20Ali%20Internation%20Service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20got%20job%20offers%20from%20Thailand%20and%20Laos%20through%20the%20firm.%20The%20company%20eventually%20sent%20him%20to%20Thailand%20where%20his%20passport%20was%20snatched%20and%20he%20was%20forced%20to%20work%20in%20a%20Chinese%20firm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Chinese%20company%20used%20to%20scan%20Indians%20online%2C%20Mr%20Lakhwat%20told%20police.%20The%20case%20was%20later%20transferred%20to%20the%20National%20Investigative%20Agency%20(NIA).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20investigation%20by%20the%20NIA%20exposed%20the%20entire%20module%20and%20it%20was%20revealed%20that%20the%20young%20men%20were%20sent%20to%20the%20Golden%20Triangle%20where%20they%20were%20forced%20to%20dupe%20Indian%2C%20European%20and%20American%20citizens%20online.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20probe%20revealed%20that%20Manzoor%20Alam%20alias%20Guddu%2C%20Sahil%2C%20Ashish%20alias%20Akhil%2C%20Pawan%20Yadav%20alias%20Afzal%20and%20their%20leader%20Zaidi%20were%20involved%20in%20the%20human%20trafficking.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20investigation%20also%20revealed%20that%20the%20people%20sent%20from%20India%20to%20foreign%20countries%20for%20jobs%20were%20treated%20poorly.%20The%20traffickers%20also%20used%20to%20extort%20money%20through%20cryptocurrency%20from%20those%20who%20tried%20to%20escape%20their%20net.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733665020000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fe01onk7o_cyber-fraud-arrested_625x300_08_December_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-500-km-chase-china-firm-that-scammed-indians-how-delhi-cops-caught-trafficker-in-india-7201562%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20man%20who%20forced%20many%20young%20men%20from%20India%20to%20commit%20cyber%20crimes%20through%20fake%20call%20centres%20on%20the%20promise%20of%20getting%20them%20jobs%20abroad%20has%20been%20arrested%20from%20Hyderabad%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20yesterday%20after%20a%202%2C500-km%20chase.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2F2-500-km-chase-china-firm-that-scammed-indians-how-delhi-cops-caught-trafficker-in-india-7201562%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Notre-Dame%20Cathedral%20Reopening%20Brings%20Together%20Emmanuel%20Macron%2C%20Donald%20Trump%20and%20Volodymyr%20Zelensky%20for%20Closed-Door%20Meeting%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1733664214000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F12%2FGettyImages-2188733176.jpg%3Fw%3D1000%26h%3D563%26crop%3D1%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236242546%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22While%20navigating%20the%20country%E2%80%99s%20worst%20political%20crisis%20since%20the%201960%E2%80%99s%2C%20French%20President%20Emmanuel%20Macron%20welcomed%20U.S.%20President-Elect%20Don