human%20slaughterhouse%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%202021%20report%20by%20the%20UK-based%20Syrian%20Observatory%20for%20Human%20Rights%2C%20over%201%20lakh%20people%20have%20been%20executed%20or%20have%20died%20in%20prisons%20of%20the%20Syrian%20regime.%20Out%20of%20them%2C%20more%20than%2030%2C000%20were%20killed%20in%20Saydnaya%20alone.%20An%20Amnesty%20International%20investigation%20found%20that%20%26quot%3Bmurder%2C%20torture%2C%20enforced%20disappearances%20and%20extermination%20carried%20out%20at%20Saydnaya%20since%202011%20have%20been%20perpetrated%20as%20part%20of%20an%20attack%20against%20the%20civilian%20population%20that%20has%20been%20widespread%2C%20as%20well%20as%20systematic%2C%20and%20carried%20out%20in%20furtherance%20of%20state%20policy%26quot%3B.%20The%20report%20said%20violations%20at%20Saydnaya%20%26quot%3Bamount%20to%20crimes%20against%20humanity%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EMass%20Hangings%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Amnesty%20report%20says%20Saydnaya%20military%20prison%20had%20two%20detention%20centres.%20A%20red%20building%20housed%20civilians%20arrested%20since%20the%20rebellion%20began%20in%202011%2C%20and%20a%20white%20building%20accommodated%20offices%20and%20soldiers%20held%20for%20their%20involvement%20in%20the%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20thousands%20of%20inmates%20in%20the%20red%20building%20have%20been%20killed%20in%20secret%20executions.%20Describing%20the%20chain%20of%20events%20in%20these%20executions%2C%20the%20report%20says%2C%20%26quot%3BBefore%20they%20are%20hanged%2C%20the%20victims%20are%20condemned%20to%20death%20in%20'trials'%20at%20the%20Military%20Field%20Court%20located%20in%20the%20al-Qaboun%20neighbourhood%20of%20Damascus%2C%20which%20last%20between%20one%20and%20three%20minutes.%20On%20the%20day%20the%20prison%20authorities%20carry%20out%20the%20hangings%2C%20which%20they%20refer%20to%20as%20'the%20party'%2C%20they%20collect%20the%20victims%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3Efrom%20their%20cells%20in%20the%20afternoon.%20The%20listed%20detainees%20are%20told%20that%20they%20will%20be%20transferred%20to%20a%20civilian%20prison.%20Instead%2C%20they%20are%20brought%20to%20a%20cell%20in%20the%20basement%20of%20the%20red%20building%2C%20where%20they%20are%20severely%20beaten%20over%20the%20course%20of%20two%20or%20three%20hours.%20In%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%2C%20they%20are%20blindfolded%20and%20transferred%20in%20delivery%20trucks%20or%20minibuses%20to%20the%20white%20building.%20There%2C%20they%20are%20taken%20into%20a%20room%20in%20the%20basement%20and%20hanged.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20takes%20place%20once%20or%20twice%20a%20week%2C%20and%20on%20each%20occasion%2C%20between%2020%20and%2050%20people%20are%20hanged%20to%20death.%20Throughout%20this%20process%2C%20the%20victims%20remain%20blindfolded.%20They%20are%20only%20told%20that%20they%20have%20been%20sentenced%20to%20death%20minutes%20before%20the%20executions%20are%20carried%20out%3B%20they%20are%20never%20told%20when%20their%20execution%20will%20be%20carried%20out%3B%20and%20they%20do%20not%20know%20how%20they%20will%20die%20until%20the%20nooses%20are%20placed%20around%20their%20necks.%20After%20the%20execution%20is%20carried%20out%2C%20the%20victims'%20bodies%20are%20loaded%20into%20a%20truck%2C%20transferred%20to%20Tishreen%20Hospital%20for%20registration%20and%20buried%20in%20mass%20graves%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOrders%20Came%20From%20The%20Top%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Amnesty%20report%2C%20prepared%20after%20speaking%20to%20people%20who%20worked%20within%20the%20prison%20and%20witness%20testimonies%20from%20those%20detained%2C%20estimated%20that%205%2C000%20and%2013%2C000%20people%20were%20extrajudicially%20executed%20at%20Saydnaya%20between%20September%202011%20and%20December%202015.%20%26quot%3BAmnesty%20International%20does%20not%20have%20evidence%20of%20executions%20after%20December%202015.%20However%2C%20detainees%20are%20still%20transferred%20to%20Saydnaya%2C%20%26quot%3Btrials%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20Military%20Field%20Court%20in%20al-Qaboun%20have%20continued%2C%20and%20there%20is%20no%20reason%20to%20believe%20that%20executions%20have%20stopped.%20Therefore%2C%20since%20December%202015%2C%20thousands%20more%20people%20are%20likely%20to%20have%20been%20executed%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20Amnesty%20report%2C%20the%20execution%20process%20at%20Saydnaya%20was%20secret%20and%20known%20only%20to%20the%20officials%20directly%20and%20high-level%20Syrian%20officials.%20%26quot%3BEven%20the%20guards%20who%20oversee%20the%20collection%20process%20and%20beatings%20at%20the%20red%20building%20are%20usually%20unaware%20of%20what%20happens%20to%20the%20detainees%20after%20they%20are%20transferred%20to%20the%20white%20building%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20night%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOfficials%20at%20the%20highest%20levels%20of%20the%20government%20authorised%20these%20death%20sentences%2C%20the%20report%20said.%20%26quot%3BDeath%20sentences%20are%20approved%20by%20the%20Grand%20Mufti%20of%20Syria%20and%20by%20either%20the%20Minister%20of%20Defence%20or%20the%20Chief%20of%20Staff%20of%20the%20Army%2C%20who%20are%20deputised%20to%20act%20on%20behalf%20of%20President%20Bashar%20al-Assad.%20The%20sentences%20are%20also%20signed%20by%20the%20head%20and%20the%20Military%20Prosecutor%20of%20the%20Military%20Field%20Court%20and%20a%20representative%20of%20the%20security%20forces.%20The%20hangings%20are%20physically%20overseen%20by%20an%20execution%20panel%2C%20which%20includes%20military%20officers%2C%20as%20well%20as%20prison%20and%20medical%20officials%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Saydnaya%20prisoners%20before%20and%20after%20their%20detention.%20Courtesy%3A%20Amnesty%20International%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Saydnaya%20prisoners%20before%20and%20after%20their%20detention.%20Courtesy%3A%20Amnesty%20International%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F60uok12o_saydnaya-prisoners_625x300_08_December_24.jpg%3Fim%3DFaceCrop%2Calgorithm%3Ddnn%2Cwidth%3D1200%2Cheight%3D738%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaydnaya%20prisoners%20before%20and%20after%20their%20detention.%20Courtesy%3A%20Amnesty%20International%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHow%20Prisoners%20Were%20Tortured%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Amnesty%20report%20said%20those%20detained%20in%20the%20red%20building%20at%20Saydnaya%20are%20subjected%20to%20an%20established%20programme%20of%20abuse.%20%26quot%3BThey%20are%20regularly%20tortured%2C%20usually%20through%20severe%20beatings%20and%20sexual%20violence.%20They%20are%20denied%20adequate%20food%2C%20water%2C%20medicine%2C%20medical%20care%20and%20sanitation%2C%20which%20has%20led%20to%20the%20rampant%20spread%20of%20infection%20and%20disease.%20Silence%20is%20enforced%2C%20even%20during%20torture%20sessions.%20Many%20detainees%20develop%20serious%20mental%20illnesses%20such%20as%20psychosis.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20says%20that%20the%20authorities'%20treatment%20of%20Saydnaya%20detainees%20%26quot%3Bseems%20designed%20to%20inflict%20maximal%20physical%20and%20psychological%20suffering%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BTheir%20apparent%20goal%20is%20to%20humiliate%2C%20degrade%2C%20dehumanize%20and%20to%20destroy%20any%20sense%20of%20dignity%20or%20hope%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Amnesty%20report%20quoted%20an%20inmate%2C%20who%20was%20a%20high-school%20student%20when%20he%20was%20arrested%2C%20%26quot%3BYou%20will%20struggle%20to%20find%20a%20former%20Saydnaya%20prisoner%20who%20will%20tell%20you%20what%20really%20happened%20there%2C%20because%20it%20is%20so%20humiliating.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20guard%20would%20ask%20everyone%20to%20take%20off%20all%20their%20clothes%20and%20go%20to%20the%20bathroom%20one%20by%20one.%20As%20we%20walked%20to%20the%20bathroom%2C%20they%20would%20select%20one%20of%20the%20boys%2C%20someone%20petite%20or%20young%20or%20fair.%20They%20would%20ask%20him%20to%20stand%20with%20his%20face%20to%20the%20door%20and%20close%20his%20eyes.%20They%20would%20then%20ask%20a%20bigger%20prisoner%20to%20rape%20him...%20No%20one%20will%20admit%20this%20happened%20to%20them%2C%20but%20it%20happened%20so%20often...%20Sometimes%2C%20psychological%20pain%20is%20worse%20than%20physical%20pain%2C%20and%20the%20people%20who%20were%20forced%20to%20do%20this%20were%20never%20the%20same%20again%2C%26quot%3B%20Omar%20said%2C%20describing%20his%20nightmare.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20detainee%20told%20Amnesty%2C%20%26quot%3BIt%20was%20as%20if%20you%20had%20a%20nail%2C%20and%20you%20were%20trying%20again%20and%20again%20to%20beat%20it%20into%20a%20rock.%20It%20was%20impossible%2C%20but%20they%20just%20kept%20going.%20I%20was%20wishing%20they%20would%20just%20cut%20off%20my%20legs%20instead%20of%20beating%20them%20any%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFreedom%20After%20Decades%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmid%20the%20regime%20change%20in%20Syria%2C%20rebel%20fighters%20have%20taken%20control%20of%20prisons%2C%20including%20Saydnaya%20and%20freed%20the%20detainees.%20A%20video%20that%20has%20gone%20viral%20shows%20a%20man%20reportedly%20freed%20from%20Saydnaya.%20He%20appears%20baffled%20and%20struggles%20to%20speak%20as%20rebels%20ask%20him%20about%20his%20family.%20NDTV%20cannot%20verify%20the%20authenticity%20of%20this%20video.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EOne%20of%20the%20detainees%20freed%20from%20Assad's%20human%20slaughterhouse%20in%20Sednaya%20has%20lost%20his%20memory%20and%20is%20unable%20to%20speak%2C%20shattered%20by%20the%20horrors%20he%20endured%2C%20Rebels%20try%20to%20ask%20him%20about%20any%20details%20to%2