documenting%20and%20sharing%20lost%20recipes%2C%20giving%20these%20flavours%20new%20life%20while%20connecting%20generations%20through%20food.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Hemlata%20Chouhan%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F386500%2Fdipali-khandelwal-kindness-meal-rajasthani-dishes-preservation-jaipur-food-heritage%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22This%20Couple%20Left%20Corporate%20Careers%20To%20Build%20an%20Organic%20Farming%20Venture%20Generating%20Rs%2090%20Lakh%2FYear%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20world%20where%20the%20corporate%20ladder%20is%20often%20seen%20as%20the%20pinnacle%20of%20success%2C%20Kotinaga%20Manikanta%20and%20Naga%20Venkata%20Durga%20Pavani%20took%20a%20bold%20and%20unconventional%20leap.%20Both%20BTech%20graduates%2C%20they%20initially%20followed%20the%20well-trodden%20path%20of%20the%20IT%20industry%20after%20completing%20their%20degrees.%20However%2C%20leaving%20behind%20the%20stability%20and%20rewards%20of%20their%20successful%20careers%2C%20this%20husband-and-wife%20duo%20from%20Guntur%2C%20Andhra%20Pradesh%2C%20traded%20boardrooms%20for%20farm%20fields%2C%20all%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F261242%2Fterrace-gardening-tips-youtube-organic-food-diet-thyroid%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epursuit%20of%20healthier%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20better%20world%20for%20farmers%20and%20consumers%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EManikanta%20worked%20at%20Infosys%2C%20and%20Pavani%20at%20Accenture%2C%20both%20carving%20out%20solid%20careers%20in%20the%20fast-paced%2C%20technology-driven%20world.%20But%20despite%20significant%20success%2C%20they%20felt%20something%20was%20missing.%20%E2%80%9CI%20saw%20many%20colleagues%20in%20the%20IT%20sector%20struggling%20with%20health%20issues%2C%20despite%20their%20well-paying%20jobs%2C%E2%80%9D%20Manikanta%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3E