-anisha-help-farmers-switch-to-organic-farmer-in-drought-prone-district%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eproducts%20from%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20delivering%20them%2C%20and%20figuring%20everything%20out%20on%20my%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20recalls%20Manikanta.%20They%20began%20by%20offering%20a%20small%20selection%20of%20organic%20items%2C%20such%20as%20mangoes%2C%20millet%20flour%2C%20%3Cem%3Etoor%20dal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20health%20mix%20powder.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBuilding%20a%20stable%20market%20for%20organic%20produce%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20building%20a%20steady%20supply%20chain%20proved%20to%20be%20one%20of%20their%20biggest%20challenges.%20At%20first%2C%20many%20farmers%20were%20hesitant%20to%20sell%20their%20produce%20through%20Sreshte.%20They%20were%20used%20to%20selling%20in%20conventional%20markets%2C%20where%20they%20received%20lower%20prices%20and%20faced%20greater%20uncertainty.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20had%20to%20convince%20them%20that%20by%20working%20together%2C%20they%20could%20get%20fair%20prices%20and%20a%20stable%20market%20for%20their%20produce%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Manikanta.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20was%20all%20about%20building%20trust.%E2%80%9D%20Despite%20the%20challenges%2C%20the%20couple%E2%80%99s%20persistence%20paid%20off%20when%20they%20opened%20their%20first%20official%20store%20in%20Guntur%20in%202019.%20By%20then%2C%20they%20had%20already%20started%20building%20a%20loyal%20customer%20base%20through%20personalised%20service%20and%20commitment%20to%20quality.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20heart%20of%20Sreshte%E2%80%99s%20model%20was%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F236549%2Fbihar-farmer-earns-lakhs-superfood-makhana-entrepreneur-lotus-seeds-fox-nuts-cultivation-farming-india-ana79%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecommitment%20to%20empowering%20farmers%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20working%20with%20local%20farmers%20already%20practising