ccess.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandy%20describes%20a%20typical%20workshop.%20%E2%80%9CUsually%2C%20when%20we%20start%20off%2C%20even%20the%20word%20%E2%80%98period%E2%80%99%20is%20taboo.%20So%2C%20we%20begin%20by%20addressing%20what%20a%20period%20is.%20We%20tell%20girls%20who%20haven%E2%80%99t%20begun%20menstruating%20by%20what%20age%20they%20should%20normally%20expect%20theirs.%20We%20help%20those%20who%20are%20actively%20menstruating%20with%20how%20to%20manage%20their%20periods%2C%20how%20to%20manage%20exercise%20in%20those%20days%20and%20stay%20hydrated.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Clabel%3EAdvertisement%3C%2Flabel%3E%5Cn%5Cn%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAll%20conversations%20are%20medically%20backed%20by%20the%20team%20of%20gynaecologists%20that%20is%20part%20of%20%E2%80%98Periods%20of%20Pride%E2%80%99.%20The%20sessions%20are%20not%20confined%20to%20theory%20but%20also%20hands-on%20workshops.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-4-1732888550.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22While%20sanitary%20pads%20are%20sometimes%20inaccessible%20in%20rural%20areas%2C%20Sandy%20Khanda%20discovered%20that%20people's%20mentality%20was%20to%20discard%20them%20in%20the%20fields%20after%20use.%20For%20this%20purpose%20he%20advocates%20cloth%20pads%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-4-1732888550.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-4-1732888550-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F11%2FSandy-Khanda-menstrual-health-4-1732888550-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%