the%20EA%E2%80%99s%20order%2C%20but%20the%20Division%20Bench%20later%20deemed%20it%20unenforceable.%20Ultimately%2C%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20upheld%20the%20EA%E2%80%99s%20order%20under%20the%20Arbitration%20Act.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%222%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-list%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EVodafone%20vs%20Indian%20Government%20(2020)%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVodafone%20initiated%20arbitration%20against%20the%20Indian%20government%20over%20a%20%E2%82%B922%2C000%20crore%20retrospective%20tax%20demand%20introduced%20by%20a%202012%20amendment%20to%20tax%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20case%2C%20heard%20at%20the%20Permanent%20Court%20of%20Arbitration%20in%20The%20Hague%2C%20concluded%20in%20Vodafone%E2%80%99s%20favour%2C%20ruling%20that%20the%20tax%20demand%20violated%20the%20bilateral%20investment%20treaty%20between%20India%20and%20the%20Netherlands.%20India%20was%20directed%20to%20refund%20legal%20costs%20and%20abandon%20its%20claim%20for%20retrospective%20taxes.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CConsumers%20are%20often%20unaware%20of%20ADR%20measures%20due%20to%20the%20misconception%20that%20ADR%20is%20time-consuming%20and%20may%20not%20yield%20optimal%20results.%20However%2C%20this%20is%20not%20entirely%20accurate.%20Better%20awareness%20is%20needed%20to%20highlight%20the%20benefits%20of%20these%20measures%20for%20consumers%2C%E2%80%9D%20notes%20Abhishek.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20choose%20arbitration%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20India%E2%80%99s%20legal%20landscape%20evolves%2C%20ADR%20mechanisms%2C%20particularly%20arbitration%2C%20are%20gaining%20traction.%20With%20laws%20like%20the%20Arbitration%20and%20Conciliation%20Act%20simplifying%20the%20process%2C%20arbitration%20is%20now%20more%20accessible%20to%20individuals%20and%20businesses%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAbhishek%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CMediation%2C%20Arbitration%2C%20and%20Lok%20Adalat%20form%20the%20pillar%20of%20reducing%20court%20burden.%E2%80%9D%20Arbitration%20offers%20a%20balanced%20approach%2C%20saving%20time%2C%20preserving%20relationships%2C%20and%20maintaining%20privacy.%20It%E2%80%99s%20the%20future%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F288718%2Ftcs-employee-fights-legal-battle-after-mass-layoff-gets-job-and-salary%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edispute%20resolution%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EEdited%20by%20Khushi%20Arora%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.barandbench.com%2Fnews%2Fparliament-watch-over-5200-vacancies-and-453-crore-pending-cases-in-lower-courts%23%3A~%3Atext%3DCase%2520pendency%2Ccases%2520(6%252C18%252C803).%26amp%3Btext%3DStates%2520with%2520the%2520highest%2520pending%2C%252C05%252C982%2520(36.05%2520lakh)%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParliament%20Watch%3A%20Over%205%2C200%20vacancies%20and%204.53%20crore%20pending%20cases%20in%20lower%20courts%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20Bar%20and%20Bench%2C%20Published%20on%2029%20November%2C%202024%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.ipleaders.in%2Fevolution-arbitration-india-lack-of-professionalism%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArbitration%20Law%20in%20India%3A%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20IPleaders%2C%20Published%20on%209%20August%2C%202024%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fblog.ipleaders.in%2Farbitration-and-conciliation-act-1996%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EArbitration%20and%20Conciliation%20Act%2C%201996%